  "html": "<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section kb-article-row-0-padding\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-2\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h1 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">Login guide</h1>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h2 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">Short introduction to the login process of the Data &amp; More Dashboard</h2>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_richtext_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_richtext_field\"><p>Data &amp; More understands the importance of easy access to your organization's dashboard or personal report. To make things simple for you, we will provide you with a convenient link that allows you to effortlessly access your desired information. This link will grant you direct access to your organization's dashboard or personal report, ensuring that you have all the data you need at your fingertips.</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-center\" height=\"485\" style=\"width: 667px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-12-9429-AM.png?width=667&amp;height=485&amp;name=image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-12-9429-AM.png\" width=\"667\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-12-9429-AM.png?width=334&amp;height=243&amp;name=image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-12-9429-AM.png 334w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-12-9429-AM.png?width=667&amp;height=485&amp;name=image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-12-9429-AM.png 667w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-12-9429-AM.png?width=1001&amp;height=728&amp;name=image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-12-9429-AM.png 1001w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-12-9429-AM.png?width=1334&amp;height=970&amp;name=image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-12-9429-AM.png 1334w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-12-9429-AM.png?width=1668&amp;height=1213&amp;name=image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-12-9429-AM.png 1668w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-12-9429-AM.png?width=2001&amp;height=1455&amp;name=image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-12-9429-AM.png 2001w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 667px) 100vw, 667px\"></p>\n<p>After clicking on the provided link, you will be directed to the account page where you can easily access your organization's dashboard or personal report.</p>\n<p>To proceed, simply select the option \"Sign in with Microsoft 365\" and enter your regular personal account credentials.</p>\n<p>This ensures a seamless and secure login experience. Once successfully signed in, you will have immediate access to all the relevant data and information you need.</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"508\" style=\"width: 644px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-47-1637-AM.png?width=644&amp;height=508&amp;name=image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-47-1637-AM.png\" width=\"644\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-47-1637-AM.png?width=322&amp;height=254&amp;name=image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-47-1637-AM.png 322w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-47-1637-AM.png?width=644&amp;height=508&amp;name=image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-47-1637-AM.png 644w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-47-1637-AM.png?width=966&amp;height=762&amp;name=image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-47-1637-AM.png 966w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-47-1637-AM.png?width=1288&amp;height=1016&amp;name=image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-47-1637-AM.png 1288w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-47-1637-AM.png?width=1610&amp;height=1270&amp;name=image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-47-1637-AM.png 1610w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-47-1637-AM.png?width=1932&amp;height=1524&amp;name=image-png-Nov-03-2023-07-43-47-1637-AM.png 1932w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 644px) 100vw, 644px\"></p>\n<p>If you encounter any issues during the sign-in process, please don't hesitate to reach out to our dedicated support team at support@dataandmore.com.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>",
